  "instructions": [
    "1. In a medium bowl, whisk together lemon juice and olive oil.",
    "2. Add chopped gherkin to the bowl and stir to combine.",
    "3. Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "4. Slice the torta caprese into 1-inch thick slices.",
    "5. Place a slice of torta caprese on a serving plate.",
    "6. Top with a slice of fresh mozzarella.",
    "7. Drizzle the lemon-gherkin dressing over the mozzarella.",
    "8. Sprinkle chopped basil over the top.",
    "9. Season with salt to taste.",
    "10. Serve immediately."
